The Glenn Beck Program - 09/26/13


Thursday, September 26, 2013 10:37 AM




Glenn proclaims he is tired of hypocrites in Washington and the mainstream media in light of how the press covered Ted Cruz's filibuster. Also Congressman Louie Gohmert joins the show to discuss what's going on in Washington. Plus, photographer George Lange talks about his new book.
